OL,3,CInterim PFAS limit could save Jersey
OL,4,Cfrom 'costly' regulation
OL,6,FJersey should delay reducing the legal
OL,7,Flimit for PFAS in its mains water,
OL,8,Faccording to the Health Minister,
OL,9,Fdespite previously backing a lower cap.
OL,11,FIn January, an independent scientific
OL,12,Fadvisory panel recommended cutting the
OL,13,Fisland's current legal limit of 12
OL,14,Fnanograms per litre to 4 nanograms per
OL,15,Flitre, a move backed by Deputy Tom
OL,16,FBinet at the time.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
