PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774436769
OL,3,CInterim PFAS limit could save Jersey
OL,4,Cfrom 'costly' regulation
OL,6,FHowever, now Deputy Binet wants to
OL,7,Fbring in an interim cap of 10
OL,8,Fnanograms per litre from October 2027,
OL,9,Fwith the aim of reaching 4 nanograms
OL,10,Fper litre by 2031.
OL,12,FJersey's legal limit is already far
OL,13,Flower than UK guidance, which aims to
OL,14,Fkeep PFAS levels to less than 100
OL,15,Fnanograms per litre, with the EU's
OL,16,Flegal limit set at a total 500
OL,17,Fnanograms per litre.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
