CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774436769
OL,3,CInterim PFAS limit could save Jersey
OL,4,Cfrom 'costly' regulation
OL,6,FEarlier this month, Jersey Water said
OL,7,Fbringing the current limit down to 4
OL,8,Fnanograms per litre could cost between
OL,9,F#140 million and #210 million as the
OL,10,Fcompany trials different methods for
OL,11,Fremoving more PFAS from mains water,
OL,12,Fwith concerns being raised about
OL,13,Fislanders' water bills potentially
OL,14,Fbeing doubled as a result.
OL,16,FIn an amendment to draft regulations,
OL,17,FDeputy Binet says introducing the cap
OL,18,Ftoo early 'risks locking Jersey into a
OL,19,Fcostly and potentially suboptimal long-
OL,20,Fterm pathway.'
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774436769
OL,3,CInterim PFAS limit could save Jersey
OL,4,Cfrom 'costly' regulation
OL,6,FHe adds: 'At the same time, Jersey
OL,7,Ffaces significant water resource
OL,8,Fpressures requiring investment'.
OL,10,FThe Minister says an interim limit
OL,11,Fwould be more a 'more measured, phased
OL,12,Fapproach' and give Jersey Water more
OL,13,Ftime to carry out the trials and make
OL,14,Fbetter informed decisions over funding
OL,15,Fany changes going forward.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
