OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774436769
OL,3,CInterim PFAS limit could save Jersey
OL,4,Cfrom 'costly' regulation
OL,6,FThe World Health Organisation (WHO)
OL,7,Fhas not yet completed its own
OL,8,Fassessment of the health risks
OL,9,Fassociated with PFAS, with final
OL,10,Fresults not expected to be published
OL,11,Funtil 2027 or 2028.
OL,13,FDeputy Binet's comments come after
OL,14,FJersey Water endorsed the Treasury
OL,15,FMinister's suggestion of an interim
OL,16,FPFAS cap of 10 nanograms per litre,
OL,17,Falthough Deputy Binet believes the 4
OL,18,Fnanogram per litre goal should still
OL,19,Fbe reached by 2031.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
